e-height:30px;\" /> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\"> 大学海报平台，旨在将各个协会的管理者从日常事务中解放出来，将更多的心思和精力花在协会的创新发展与开拓进取上。</span><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;word-break:normal;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\" /> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><a href=\"http://huodong.ustc.edu.cn/static/help/aboutusd.htm\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;word-break:normal;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;color:#0000ff;text-decoration:none;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;cursor:pointer;\">点击查看详细图文介绍</a><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;word-break:normal;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\" /> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\"> </span><a href=\"http://home.ustc.edu.cn/~wyqq/a/index.html\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;word-break:normal;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;color:#0000ff;text-decoration:none;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;cursor:pointer;\">点击查看网站使用效果演示</a><span style=\"font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\"> </span><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;word-break:normal;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\" /> &nbsp; &nbsp;<br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;word-break:normal;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\" /><span style=\"font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\">预期开发版本介绍</span><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;word-break:normal;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\" /> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\">Beta1版本： 实现海报发布、社团主页、成员列表、群邮件、社团招新功能开发</span><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;word-break:normal;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\" /> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\">Beta2版本： 毕业季、项目组建立、短信通知规则、活动介绍富文本编辑、时间轴功能</span><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;word-break:normal;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\" /> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\">Beta3版本： 高校间社团的交互区域、需求对接区域等个性化板块的开发</span><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;word-break:normal;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\" /> &nbsp; &nbsp;<br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;word-break:normal;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\" /> &nbsp; &nbsp;<br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;word-break:normal;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\" /><span style=\"font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\">开发团队：（<span style=\"font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;color:#ff0000;\">排名不分先后，姓氏首字母排序</span>）</span><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;word-break:normal;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\" /> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\">李博杰（Linux协会会长）网站后台开发</span><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;word-break:normal;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\" /> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\">马琼 （网工办负责人） 负责联系协助推广</span><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;word-break:normal;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\" /> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\">王艳秋（创业协会会长） 网站整体设计、外观设计与前台开发</span><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;word-break:normal;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\" /> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\">王晶晶（百度俱乐部部长）网站后台开发、服务器升级管理</span><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;word-break:normal;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\" /> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\">其它参与开发的同学：刘春山（前台）、林太星（后台）</span><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;word-break:normal;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\" /> &nbsp; &nbsp;<br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;word-break:normal;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\" /> &nbsp; &nbsp;<br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;word-break:normal;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\" /><span style=\"font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\">支持组织介绍</span><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;word-break:normal;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\" /> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\">校网工办、政研室</span><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;word-break:normal;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\" /> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\">中国科大学生创业协会</span><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;word-break:normal;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\" /> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\">中国科大学生Linux用户协会</span><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;word-wrap:break-word;word-break:normal;font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;, &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\" /> &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:&#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;font-size:18px;line-height:30px;\">中国科大学生百度俱乐部</span></p>'),(77,2,'club',377,'active',0,'a','a','','','','','','',NULL,10,10,1,0,'','<p>在此编辑社团的详细介绍。可以上传图片、自由排版哦！</p>');
